_sText:
Introducing gg_desert_dilapidation_v2!
This is a fun and fast paced gun game map I threw together while I was drunk one night lol.It is pretty simply decorated and laid out, however, I have received positive reviews regarding it in test plays. It is possible to get to the boards on the roof by jumping to the ladders on the side of the building. It holds up to 24 players in it, any more than that the match would get pretty cramped : )
Have Fun!

       -Monty
